# MCP Integration Scripts

This directory contains scripts that leverage existing MCP servers to provide functionality similar to unavailable MCP packages.

## Scripts

- `playwright-integration.ts` - Playwright test generation using filesystem-ops + sequential-thinking
- `vitest-integration.ts` - Vitest test analysis using typescript-enhanced + git-integration
- `sentry-integration.ts` - Sentry monitoring using filesystem-ops + context7
- `github-integration.ts` - GitHub workflow automation using git-integration + filesystem-ops

## Usage

All scripts follow the pattern:

```bash
pnpm tsx scripts/mcp-integrations/<script-name>.ts [options]
```

See individual script files for specific usage instructions.
